## 6. Category Picker & Inline Create

- [x] Personal line → shows only that member's personal categories
- [x] HH Obligation line → shows only that member's assigned obligation categories
- [x] HH Shared line → shows household shared categories (admin only)
- [x] Project line → shows active project list only
- [x] "Add new category" expander for personal target → entering parent + sub + budget and clicking Create → new category appears in the picker on next reload of the review screen
- [x] "Add new category" for `hh_shared` → non-admin sees "Only admins can create Household categories" message, no form
- [OYfDaFoR7MLHYqDbXtivnQ] "Add new category" for project → shows "Projects are managed in the Projects module" message, no form

---

## 7. Save Draft

- [x] Clicking Save Draft without posting → "Draft saved." confirmation; no expense rows appear in Budget → Expenses
- [x] Resuming the draft afterward shows the same lines in the same state

---

## 8. Post to Ledger — Happy Paths

- [x] Personal line with category → expense appears in that member's Personal ledger under the selected category
- [x] HH Obligation line with category → expense appears in the Household ledger under the obligation category; member's personal ledger reflects it if integration is on
- [x] HH Shared line with category (admin) → expense appears in the Household shared budget
- [x] Project line with project selected → project actual cost increments; expense logged under the Projects category
- [x] All lines posted successfully → receipt status changes to posted; review screen closes and returns to the upload form

---

## 9. Post to Ledger — Uncategorized Fallback

- [x] Allow uncategorized ON (default): posting a personal line with no category selected → Receipt / Uncategorized personal category is auto-created and the expense lands there
- [x] Allow uncategorized ON: posting an HH Shared line with no category → Receipt / Uncategorized HH category created; expense lands there
- [x] Allow uncategorized OFF: posting any line with no category → error message "Category required. Select a category or enable uncategorized posting."
- [x] HH Obligation line with no category → always blocked regardless of the uncategorized toggle (no safe default bucket)
- [x] Project line with no project selected → always blocked with "No project selected for this line."
- [x] Expenses in Receipt / Uncategorized are visible and editable in Budget → Expenses (one-time expenses list) for later recategorization

---

## 10. Partial Post & Error Recovery

- [x] Mix of valid and invalid lines (e.g., one personal line ready, one obligation line without a category) → valid line posts; failed line shows inline error; review screen stays open with failed lines editable
- [x] After fixing a failed line, clicking Post again → remaining line posts; receipt marked posted

---

## 11. Permission Guardrails (server-side)

- [x] Regular member cannot select `hh_shared` or project ledger target (UI hides them; even if tampered, DB write returns false)
- [x] Member posting to an obligation category not in their assignment list → `log_household_expense_from_personal` rejects it; error shown
- [x] Receipt draft not visible to another household member who didn't upload it (and is not admin)

---

## 12. Edge Cases

- [x] Uploading a second receipt while a draft is already open → draft list shows both; each resumes independently
- [x] Receipt with a single line item → posts normally (no "empty lines" error)
- [x] Line amount of $0.00 or blank → blocked with "Amount must be greater than zero" at post time
- [x] Very long description (200+ chars) → truncated gracefully; does not break the layout
